<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge" />
    <title>ESHOP ONLINE Seller Account Verification</title>
    <style>
      /* Reset */
      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto,
          Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.7;
        background-color: #f4f6fb;
        color: #2d3748;
      }

      .wrapper {
        background-color: #f4f6fb;
        padding: 30px 0;
        width: 100%;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 16px;
        box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      .header {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb 0%, #1d4ed8 100%);
        padding: 40px 0;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .logo {
        font-size: 32px;
        color: #ffffff;
        font-weight: 800;
        text-decoration: none;
        letter-spacing: -1px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      .content {
        padding: 48px 40px;
        text-align: left;
      }

      h1 {
        color: #1a202c;
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .greeting {
        font-size: 18px;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
        color: #4a5568;
      }

      p {
        color: #4a5568;
        font-size: 16px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      .otp-container {
        background: #f0f4ff;
        border: 1px solid #cbd5e1;
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 32px;
        margin: 32px 0;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .otp-code {
        font-family: "Courier New", Courier, monospace;
        font-size: 36px;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 8px;
        color: #2563eb;
        background: #ffffff;
        padding: 16px 24px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        border: 2px dashed #cbd5e1;
        display: inline-block;
      }

      .expiry-notice {
        background-color: #fffbf0;
        border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;
        padding: 16px 24px;
        margin: 24px 0;
        border-radius: 8px;
      }

      .warning-icon {
        color: #d97706;
        margin-right: 8px;
      }

      .highlight {
        color: #2563eb;
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      .divider {
        height: 1px;
        background-color: #e2e8f0;
        margin: 32px 0;
      }

      .footer {
        background-color: #f8fafc;
        padding: 32px 40px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .footer p {
        color: #718096;
        font-size: 14px;
        margin: 8px 0;
      }

      .social-links {
        margin-top: 24px;
      }

      .social-links a {
        color: #2563eb;
        text-decoration: none;
        margin: 0 8px;
      }

      @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
        .content {
          padding: 32px 24px;
        }

        .otp-container {
          padding: 24px 16px;
        }

        .otp-code {
          font-size: 32px;
          letter-spacing: 6px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="wrapper">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
          <div class="logo">ESHOP ONLINE</div>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
          <h1>Verify Your Seller Account</h1>
          <p class="greeting">Hello <%= name %>,</p>
          <p>
            Welcome to ESHOP ONLINE! We're thrilled to have you join our seller
            community. To secure your account, please verify your email with the
            code below:
          </p>

          <div class="otp-container">
            <div class="otp-code"><%= otp %></div>
            <p style="margin-top: 16px; font-size: 14px; color: #718096">
              Enter this code on the verification page to proceed
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="expiry-notice">
            <span class="warning-icon">⚠️</span>
            This verification code will expire in
            <span class="highlight">5 minutes</span> for security reasons.
          </div>

          <p>
            If you did not create a seller account, please ignore this email or
            contact support if you believe this is an error.
          </p>

          <div class="divider"></div>

          <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #718096">
            Need help? Contact our support team at
            <a
              href="mailto:support@eshoponline.com"
              style="color: #2563eb; text-decoration: none"
              >support@eshoponline.com</a
            >
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
          <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply.</p>
          <p>
            &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> ESHOP ONLINE. All rights
            reserved.
          </p>
          <div class="social-links">
            <a href="#">Twitter</a> • <a href="#">Facebook</a> •
            <a href="#">Instagram</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
